  <brief_title>High Dose of Dual Therapy Plus Bismuth for Helicobacter Pylori Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of High Dose of Dual Therapy Plus Bismuth for Helicobacter Pylori Treatment：a Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
