  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Dual therapy for Helicobacter Pylori including a proton pump inhibitor (PPI) and amoxicillin.
      Amoxicillin has low resistance rate as well as low percentage of side effects. No trial has
      examined the the efficacy of high dose of dual therapy plus bismuth for H. pylori
      treatment.This study is designed to evaluate the efficacy and safety of the addition of
      bismuth to high dose of dual therapy for H. pylori eradication.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
